description: If you’re feeling the heat in Southern Maine, you’re in luck because Robyn’s Ice Cream Truck is hittin’ the streets and serving up an insane selection of delicious ice cream!Robyn’s carries all your favorites from Popsicle, Klondike, Blue Bunny, and more, and they will happily haul this creamy goodness all the way to your door so that you can treat your friends, family, or community to a day of refreshing and tasty frozen fun.
name: Robyn's Ice Cream
